96
00:07:52,287 --> 00:07:54,186
- at the site at Namil. - Gosh...

97
00:07:54,186 --> 00:07:56,027
Gosh!

98
00:07:56,287 --> 00:07:58,587
It's receiving so much attention,

99
00:07:58,587 --> 00:08:01,727
