101
00:08:05,266 --> 00:08:06,337
Cheer up.

102
00:08:06,766 --> 00:08:08,766
The world is slowly changing.

103
00:08:09,337 --> 00:08:11,436
It's not like it's anything new to us.

104
00:08:12,066 --> 00:08:13,176
Cheer up.

105
00:08:13,176 --> 00:08:14,337
Everyone, look!

106
00:08:14,676 --> 00:08:17,707
Ms. Doh got her official permission. Congratulations!

107
00:08:17,707 --> 00:08:18,777
