108
00:08:19,246 --> 00:08:21,176
"Research Team Leader Doh Joong Eun".

109
00:08:21,176 --> 00:08:23,787
Ms. Gong, may I see you?

110
00:08:25,147 --> 00:08:26,417
Congratulations.

111
00:08:30,927 --> 00:08:36,727
(Undiagnosed Disease Center)

112
00:08:43,837 --> 00:08:47,036
