118
00:09:30,746 --> 00:09:32,587
(Kim Do Hyeong)

119
00:09:35,217 --> 00:09:36,656
Hello.

120
00:09:45,197 --> 00:09:46,437
Thank you.

121
00:10:35,246 --> 00:10:36,987
