122
00:10:36,987 --> 00:10:38,746
I'm sorry I'm late.

123
00:10:38,746 --> 00:10:40,016
Why are you late?

124
00:10:40,016 --> 00:10:43,927
My other part-time job ran late.

125
00:10:43,927 --> 00:10:46,427
This won't ever happen again. I'm sorry.

126
00:10:49,327 --> 00:10:51,866
Mr. Moh, we've taken good care of it.

127
00:10:51,866 --> 00:10:54,266
We got a waste exporter who works with China,

128
00:10:54,266 --> 00:10:55,666
