129
00:10:55,666 --> 00:10:56,866
Go ahead!

130
00:11:05,677 --> 00:11:07,217
Good job, Mr. Jung.

131
00:12:34,467 --> 00:12:37,266
(TL Medical Center)

132
00:12:37,766 --> 00:12:41,707
There was an uproar at the Planning and Strategy Team.

133
00:12:43,207 --> 00:12:45,276
Leave him to be.

134
00:12:45,677 --> 00:12:47,146
That's it, sir.

135
00:12:47,146 --> 00:12:48,977
And you have mail, sir.

136
00:12:48,977 --> 00:12:50,886
It's only from the people on the list.

137
00:12:53,786 --> 00:12:55,286
No need for this.

138
00:12:55,286 --> 00:12:56,357
(Choi Seo Rin)

139
