144
00:13:19,746 --> 00:13:21,347
(An eye for an eye, a tooth for a tooth.)

145
00:13:21,347 --> 00:13:22,987
(You'll suffer the same!)

146
00:13:24,516 --> 00:13:25,847
Mr. Kwon.

147
00:13:27,587 --> 00:13:29,526
