180
00:15:43,156 --> 00:15:46,396
Are we holding this meeting to carry out Mr. Moh's orders?

181
00:15:47,827 --> 00:15:49,396
Are we here to only talk about Oshem?

182
00:15:51,927 --> 00:15:54,567
