203
00:16:59,967 --> 00:17:01,296
He's lost his mind.

204
00:17:01,566 --> 00:17:03,506
He obviously feels cornered.

205
00:17:03,506 --> 00:17:04,967
How dare he call me a minion?

206
00:17:08,036 --> 00:17:09,237
As for the price reduction strategy,

207
00:17:09,606 --> 00:17:11,106
there's an 80-percent chance that it'll fail.

208
00:17:11,447 --> 00:17:14,617
He should clearly give up, but he kept on pushing for it.

209
00:17:15,346 --> 00:17:16,586
Don't be so upset.

210
00:17:17,586 --> 00:17:21,516
You got half of the job done by mentioning UDC.

211
00:17:25,286 --> 00:17:27,627
Good work today.

212
