217
00:18:43,437 --> 00:18:46,167
Oh, my. Look at you, Seo Rin.

218
00:18:46,437 --> 00:18:49,237
You can draw so well.

219
00:18:51,207 --> 00:18:52,246
Seo Rin.

220
00:18:53,417 --> 00:18:55,316
Can you write your name?

221
00:18:55,947 --> 00:18:57,947
Write, "Choi Seo Rin".

222
00:18:58,217 --> 00:18:59,387
Here, right here.

223
00:19:02,657 --> 00:19:04,457
(Choi Seo Rin)

224
00:19:06,526 --> 00:19:07,727
Choi...

225
00:19:09,727 --> 00:19:12,467
Seo Rin.

226
00:19:13,137 --> 00:19:14,667
(Choi Seo Rin)

227
00:19:15,137 --> 00:19:16,197
And a heart.

228
00:19:19,707 --> 00:19:20,737
Seo Rin.

229
00:19:21,877 --> 00:19:24,147
You wrote this, right?

230
00:19:25,806 --> 00:19:28,516
Who is it for?

231
00:19:30,387 --> 00:19:31,417
I don't know.

232
00:19:39,286 --> 00:19:41,927
