233
00:19:41,927 --> 00:19:43,127
(n-Hexane)

234
00:19:53,106 --> 00:19:54,506
(To Mom)

235
00:19:54,707 --> 00:19:57,046
(Choi Seo Rin)

236
00:20:05,217 --> 00:20:07,157
