249
00:20:52,427 --> 00:20:53,496
UDC?

250
00:20:54,437 --> 00:20:55,437
Is that so?

251
00:20:55,437 --> 00:20:56,667
(Choi Seo Rin)

252
00:20:57,667 --> 00:20:59,606
